title: Recently Remodeled Eureka Valley 1BR + Office!
posting_body: ['$3,195 | 4401 20th St, San Francisco, CA 94114', 'Coming Soon!', 'Recently Remodeled Eureka Valley 1BR + Office!', 'Available August 7th!', 'Gorgeous 1+ Bedroom/1 Bathroom in the heart of the Eureka Valley.', 'This beautiful and recently remodeled residence boasts an updated kitchen with designer finishes and stainless-steel appliances including a gas range, dishwasher and refrigerator.', 'The beautifully remodeled bathroom includes a walk-in shower with decorative tile surround and a new vanity with medicine cabinet.', '  This residence can be used as a one bedroom plus office for your WFH needs or set it up as a flexible two bedroom.', ' Excellent location just a few short blocks to the shops, restaurants and excitement of Castro Village and Noe Valley’s 24th', 'Street - Public transportation, Tech Shuttle stops and park space very close by!', 'KEY FEATURES:', '– New hardwood floors throughout', '– Newly remodeled Kitchen and Bathroom', '-In-Unit Washer/Dryer', '-Dishwasher', '-Period detail, decorative wainscotting and built-ins', '-Additional office space or second bedroom', '-Shared back garden', 'TERMS:', '1 year lease', 'Rent-controlled building', 'Security Deposit = 1 month + $500', 'Tenant pays all utilities', 'Available August 7th!', 'Contact Brett for more information or to schedule a tour!', 'Brett van den Eikhof', 'DRE #01910306', 'brett@gaetanirealestate (.) com', 'For more units available, visit <URL>', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by tenant of their rights under the rent ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.']
